sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Go runner
    participant L as Lean engine
    participant A as Local or ACP agent
    participant H as Helper tools

    Note over A: ACP roles get one transient home only.<br/>No repo mount, run directory mount,<br/>or persistent host state mount.

    R->>L: role_view(state, role)
    L-->>R: visible case view
    R->>A: prompt with role preamble,<br/>role view, tool cards, current opportunity

    loop same opportunity
        A->>H: _adc/get_case, _adc/get_juror_context,<br/>_adc/list_case_files, _adc/read_case_text_file,<br/>_adc/request_case_file
        H->>L: role_view-backed visibility checks
        L-->>H: visible data only
        H-->>A: helper result

        A->>R: _adc/submit_decision(pass or tool)
        R->>L: apply_decision(state, opportunity, decision)
        alt invalid
            L-->>R: StepErr with actor_message
            R-->>A: correction message
        else valid
            L-->>R: accepted action or pass
            R->>L: step(state, action) when action was accepted
            L-->>R: updated state
        end
    end
